name: Naughty Kid - Snowball Edition
summary: Become the ultimate winter troublemaker in this fun, fast-paced VR snowball experience! You play as the pampered child of wealthy parents—bored, unsupervised, and ready to stir up a bit of mischief. Armed with an endless supply of perfectly packed snowballs, your mission is simple: aim, throw, and see how many unsuspecting pedestrians you can hit before time runs out.
